These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, 7up, coffee, lemonade, milk
6 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, guinea-pig, rabbit, hamster, dog
 1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Beverage   | coffee | milk | mirinda    | almond-milk | 7up | lemonade |
| Pet        | turtle      | dog  | rabbit | frog | hamster          | guinea-pig  |

