.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola, almond-milk, sprite, fanta
There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian, egyptian, polish, australian, chinese
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 3. the polish is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 4. the polish is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 5. the australian is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the egyptian##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking water and the person drinking lemonade##2
 8. the chinese is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the polish is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the australian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
12. the canadian is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
13. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
14. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | water  | almond-milk     | lemonade | cola    | fanta       | sprite  |
| Nationality   | chinese | indonesian | egyptian       | polish | canadian | australian |

