.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  mechanic, chef, bartender, photographer, security-guard, manager
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, roller, helicopter, trike, boat, car
1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
2. the security-guard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the mechanic is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the bartender is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
5. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
6. the photographer is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
7. the chef is between the photographer and the bartender##2
8. the security-guard is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4     |    5     |     6     |
| Job         | photographer | chef | bartender | security-guard | mechanic  | manager    |
| Transport   | car      | helicopter  | boat  | roller       | subway | trike |

