.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, sprite, milk, lemonade, coffee
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, collecting, singing, sudoku, traveling, magic-tricks
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person drinking lemonade##2
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | coffee     | lemonade | mirinda        | milk   | sprite |
| Hobby      | baking | traveling | singing  | collecting | magic-tricks | sudoku       |

