.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-5::.
There 6 different types of food: corn, blueberry, banana, pumpkin, pepper, tomato
There are 6 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, british, malaysian, russian, thai
1. the person eating banana is between the person eating corn and the person eating pepper##2
2. the thai is on the left or right of the british##3
3. the russian is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
4. the thai is the person eating blueberry##1
5. the british is on the far right##1
6. the colombian is the person eating pepper##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the far left##1
9. the colombian is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
| Food          | tomato | pepper | banana | corn | blueberry | pumpkin   |
| Nationality   | russian   | colombian   | canadian    | malaysian | thai    | british |

