.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, musician, dressmaker, mechanic, chef, teacher
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, handball, cricket, surfing, biathlon, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the manager##3
 2. the manager is between the person who's sport is surfing and the teacher##2
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 5. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 7. the manager is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 9. the teacher is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the musician is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | musician        | mechanic | teacher | manager  | dressmaker  | chef |
| Sport   | cricket | handball   | badminton  | basketball | surfing | biathlon          |

