.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, turtle, frog, bird, cat
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, bike, skateboard, trike, motorbike
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person driving the trike is the owner of the frog##1
10. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the frog and the person driving the bus##2
11. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | cat | turtle      | frog | bird | mouse | pony |
| Transport   | bus  | helicopter | trike   | motorbike        | bike   | skateboard |

