.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, milk, lemonade, coffee, sprite
The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, baking, board-games, card-games, gardening, dancing
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |   3   |    4     |    5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | sprite     | lemonade | milk | soy-milk    | coffee        |
| Hobby      | board-games   | card-games | fishing | gardening   | dancing | baking |

