 4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the indian##3
 5. the owner of the fish is the polish##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the indian##3
 7. the russian is the owner of the goat##1
 8. the russian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the polish is between the nigerian and the owner of the cat##2
10. the owner of the horse is the indian##1
