.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-10::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, milk, coffee, iced-tea, cola
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing, water-polo, cycling, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
9. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4     |      5      |       6       |
| Beverage   | cola  | iced-tea | sprite     | coffee    | water | milk |
| Sport      | skateboarding | golf   | cycling | water-polo | skiing    | snowboarding       |

