 5. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 8. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
11. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2   |   3    |   4    |      5      |     6     |
