 5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 6. the fan of indie is on the left of the thai##1
 7. the malaysian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 8. the thai is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 9. the fan of techno is the canadian##1
10. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
