The people use 6 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, motorbike, snowmobile, bike, car
 1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating avocado is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the scooter##2
 8. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating strawberry##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person eating potato is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |    3     |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Food        | potato  | avocado | orange | mango | strawberry   | pumpkin |
| Transport   | scooter | motorbike | snowmobile    | bike     | skateboard | car    |

