.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-16::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, mirinda, sprite, fanta, lemonade
There 6 different types of food: raspberry, grapefruit, cucumber, potato, strawberry, pineapple
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 3. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking lemonade and the person eating potato##2
 4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking fanta##2
 8. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
10. the person eating strawberry is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking fanta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |      3      |   4   |  5   |   6   |
| Beverage   | sprite | mirinda | coffee | fanta | tea | lemonade |
| Food       | cucumber   | pineapple        | raspberry     | potato | strawberry | grapefruit  |

