.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-17::.
There 6 different types of food: pineapple, broccoli, apple, strawberry, banana, lettuce
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: drama, musical, time-travel, adventure, action, crime
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 6. the person eating lettuce is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person eating apple is between the person watching drama movies and the person eating strawberry##2
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |    5    |     6     |
| Food          | banana     | apple         | strawberry  | broccoli | pineapple | lettuce |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | time-travel | crime | action   | musical  | adventure    |

