The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skiing, parkour, badminton, soccer, volleyball, golf
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |    5    |      6      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | drawing | baking | card-games     | singing | traveling |
| Sport   | parkour    | soccer  | badminton   | skiing | volleyball   | golf    |

 